  "title": "Senior Interior Designer",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring Junior/Senior Interior Designers !</p>\n<p>Drop us an email with your resume today!</p>\n<p>Email: info@urbanhomedesign.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>understand homeowner requirement and propose space planning with layout and material</em></li>\n  <li><em>draw in 2D CAD &amp; 3D Sketch Up</em></li>\n  <li><em>responsible to work out quotation</em></li>\n  <li><em>responsible to supervise work progress and meet the timeline</em></li>\n  <li><em>responsible to liaise with suppliers and subcontractors in order to have good quality works</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>O level(Min), Diploma, Degree/Bachelor</em></li>\n  <li><em>Min 1 years’ experience in interior design or construction project management or related experience</em></li>\n  <li><em>Strong problem solving and analytical skills</em></li>\n  <li><em>Able to converse in English and Mandarin(in order to handle queries and concerns from English and Chinese speaking counterparts in regards with the interior design related matters.)</em></li>\n  <li><em>Creative, independent, self-discipline, willing to learn, love to talk to customer and meticulous</em></li>\n  <li><em>Good communication and like to do presentation, able to meet client at weekend and public holidays</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Why join us?</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>SIDA Best Design Award Winner</em></li>\n  <li><em>Singapore Good Design Award Winner</em></li>\n  <li><em>Golden Pin Design Award Winner</em></li>\n  <li><em>IF Design Award </em></li>\n  <li><em>Qanvast Top 3 Interior Design Firm</em></li>\n  <li><em>SuperTrust Award Winner Interior Design Firm</em></li>\n  <li><em>Well-Known Boutique Interior Design Firm</em></li>\n  <li><em>New 3500sf Design Show Room</em></li>\n  <li><em>Plenty of opportunities to grow as a pioneer in our company</em></li>\n  <li><em>Salary based or Profit sharing based</em></li>\n</ul>",
